Class InitializeMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • DBAccess.InitializeMapper
  • public class InitializeMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    The purpose of the InitializeMapper class is to communicate with the Database with SQL statements to retrieve carport and shed measurements from the database.

    Pelle Rasmussen
